<h2 class="mt-10 mb-3" id="orisa">Orisa</h2>

<h3 class="mb-1">Against</h3>
<span class="text-small mb-2 font-italic">Duels: Good | Teamfights: Great</span>

<p>
  Orisa is often incorrectly seen as a counter to Mei because of her Fortify. While this ability does of course prevent her from being stunned, Mei does still counter her on every front.
</p>

<p class="mb-1">
  Often times you will find Orisa at a distance with her team hiding behind her shield. To counter this shield you can simply place your Icewall right inside of it. This forces the enemy to either wait out your Icewall while your team pushes the objective or repositions for a better angle, or move away from the shield and expose themselves. The Orisa will likely reposition her shield to a worse position, leaving them more vulnerable the moment your Icewall goes down.<br>
  Another option is to try and single out a target. Place your Icewall under an enemy and lift him up away from the safety of the shield. You will not have a lot of time to react so make sure your team is ready and aware of what you are doing. With proper focus you can quickly take out enemies or at the very least force them to use valuable abilities. <br>
</p>

